179    /**
180    * This class provides the core API provider functionality. It is implemented in a very
181    * self-contained and 'pure' manner, without taking requirements like security into account,
182    * which are subject to frequent change. Due to this 'pure' nature and the significance of
183    * the class to the overall API management functionality, the visibility of the class has
184    * been reduced to package level. This means we can still use it for internal purposes and
185    * possibly even extend it, but it's totally off the limits of the users. Users wishing to
